<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>某一个深夜，在美罗城公园里的湖里，青蛙呱呱叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然一个发光体从天上掉下来，扑通一声掉进湖里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>湖面上冒起很多泡泡，湖水变成了紫色。呱呱！呱呱！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，罗西和朋友们在美罗城公园的小树林里玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们瞧！”特勒尔站在大石头上喊道，“我比你们都高！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也要上去！” 玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也要！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个女孩儿开始往上爬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"我不要！"杰克说，“我不喜欢高的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是害怕高的地方吗？”玛拉问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是害怕。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是不喜欢待在高的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔耸耸肩。“那也没什么。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就不喜欢黑的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我害怕怪物。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尤其是有尖牙的怪物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没什么好怕的”。特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"火箭女孩儿会保护我们的。"</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着罗西问：“罗西，你害怕什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，玛拉大喊道：“你们看！树叶下面有一只青蛙！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉从石头上跳下来，捡起小青蛙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔和杰克走过来。“呃！呃！”罗西叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么了？”玛拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"别让那只青蛙靠近我。"罗西说，“好恶心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是害怕青蛙吧？”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是害怕。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是觉得它们......很恶心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说不定火箭女孩儿能帮你。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“帮我？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”特勒尔说，“让你不再害怕青蛙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西皱着眉头说：“我说了我不是——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呱呱！呱呱！“那是什么声音？”杰克边问，边看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听起来像是青蛙。”特勒尔说，“不过声音太大了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边一棵树倒了。哐！又一棵树倒了。哐！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们吓得大气不敢出，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看到一只巨大的动物，正在慢慢靠近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那......那是一只青蛙！”特勒尔大叫！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只巨型青蛙！”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比车还大！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呱呱！那只巨型青蛙跃向天空，消失不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的脸变得苍白。很快她的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西避开朋友们，按下按钮，布洛姆市长出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我猜猜看，市长先生。”罗西低声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是因为那只巨型青蛙来找我的吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不只是一只，火箭女孩儿！”市长喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到处都是巨型青蛙！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们正在入侵美罗城！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请你想想办法！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>